Quickstrike:




Quickstrike came to sense after Double Punch came to sight. He watched as 
Ramulus attacked the Predacon. He took this oppertunity to grab Dark Mouse. 
He bent over, watching his own sides. He put his arm around her waist, and 
lifted her. He stared at the Predacon base. It was going to be one Inferno 
of a sprint. It seemed like everyone was after this mouse-bot.

He took off. "Scorponok, flank me!"
